sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.windbg

Interface WindbgDebugger

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Debugger, JVMDebugger, SymbolLookup, ThreadAccess
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WindbgDebuggerLocal

    public interface WindbgDebugger
extends JVMDebugger
    An extension of the JVMDebugger interface with a few additions to support 32-bit vs. 64-bit debugging as well as features required by the architecture-specific subpackages.
